
Item.create(name:'Marc Jacobs Velvet Noir Major Volume Mascara' , description:'Experience ultimate volume and the look of thick, false lashes with Velvet Noir Major Volume Mascara. The lash-maximizing, curvy brush places the most volume at the hard-to-reach center lash line, and the defining tip styles lashes for major drama. The super-concentrated black pigment delivers the greatest visual impact, and the Flash Volume Complex™ creates instant, smudge-proof length and volume in three strokes or less. Velvet Noir gives you the thickest lashes in one sweep. Apply Velvet Noir Major Volume Mascara on its own, or layer with O!Mega Lash Volumizing Mascara (sold separately). Pair it with Feather Noir Ultra-Skinny Lash-Discovering Mascara and Lamé Noir Ultra-Glittering Mascara (sold separately) to style your lashes for every occasion.', image_url:'http://www.beautyjunkiesunite.com/WP/wp-content/uploads/2016/01/MARC-jacobs-velvet-noir-major-volume-mascara.jpg',buy_url:'http://www.sephora.com/velvet-noir-major-volume-mascara-P403806').tags.create(name: "Mascara")
Item.create(name:'Tarte Lights, Camera, Lashes™ 4-in-1 Mascara' , description:'Tarte lights, camera, lashes™ 4-in-1 mascara could be considered a dramatic makeover for your lashes. This high-performance formula is proven to increase the appearance of lash volume by 330 percent—creating strikingly thick, sexy lashes.',image_url:'http://www.sephora.com/productimages/sku/s1674001-main-hero-300.jpg',buy_url:'http://www.sephora.com/lights-camera-lashes-P111902?skuId=862417').tags.create(name: "Mascara")
Item.create(name: 'Bobbi BrownEye Opening Mascara',description:'Create the ultimate lifted, faux lash look, from root to tip, with Bobbi Brown’s Eye Opening Mascara. Designed exclusively for this mascara, its jumbo brush head grabs and visibly pushes each and every lash upwards, leaving a long-lasting curl that holds for eight hours.',image_url:'http://g.nordstromimage.com/ImageGallery/store/product/Large/4/_6345084.jpg' ,     buy_url:'http://www.sephora.com/eye-opening-mascara-P403974?skuId=1780667').tags.create(name: "Mascara")
Item.create(name:'Philosophy Purity Made Simple',description:'Begin with the most basic step of all. Purity Made Simple one-step facial cleanser is an award-winning cleanser that melts away dirt, oil, and makeup. It tones and lightly hydrates in one simple step for skin that feels perfectly clean and comfortably balanced. Formulated for all skin types and gentle enough for the sensitive eye area, it deep cleans pores while natural oil extracts help condition skin.', image_url:'https://www.truthinaging.com/media/thumbnails/13970.jpg',buy_url:'http://www.sephora.com/purity-made-simple-P7109?skuId=407304').tags.create(name: "Face Wash")
Item.create(name: 'Murad Clarifying Cleanser' , description:'Clarifying Cleanser’s rich lather strips away pore-clogging grime, oil, and irritants, while encapsulated salicylic acid provides a sustained release of medication for hours of acne treatment, even after rinsing. A bestselling Murad product for nearly 20 years, this cleanser is recommended as the first step in any Murad acne routine. Clarifying Cleanser is formulated to improve skin’s health as part of Dr. Murad’s Inclusive Health® system of care.', image_url:'http://www.demeterclarc.com/wp-content/uploads/images/2012/12/MURAD-CLARIFYING-CLEANSER-PRODUCT-DISPLAY.jpg',buy_url:'http://www.sephora.com/clarifying-cleanser-P4016?skuId=654228').tags.create(name: "Face Wash")
Item.create(name:'Caolion Hot & Cool Pore Foam Cleansing Duo', description:'The Pore Blackhead Steam Foam Cleanser deep cleanses by harnessing the power of steam while natural brown sugar gently exfoliates, providing a smoother and more refined texture. As the cleanser heats up on contact, it removes impurities and dissolves dead skin cells softly without irritation—resulting in smoother and firmer-looking skin.', image_url:'http://www.polyvore.com/cgi/img-thing?.out=jpg&size=l&tid=159596177', buy_url:'http://www.sephora.com/hot-cool-pore-foam-cleansing-duo-P405401?skuId=1802750').tags.create(name: "Face Wash")
Item.create(name: 'Kat Von D Studded Kiss Lipstick', description:'Drench your lips with bold color and unstoppable femininity. Designed to look as rock ‘n roll as its wearer, this revolutionary, hybrid lipstick is formulated with Color Cushion Technology™, which combines lasting-wear, one-swipe payoff, and velvet-touch comfort. This color-true lipstick leaves lips supple, and its wide color spectrum offers stunning shades, including red for every skintone, statement-making colors, and classic, everyday neutrals.',image_url:'http://www.beautezine.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/07/Kat-Von-D-Studded-Kiss-Lipsticks.jpg', buy_url:'http://www.sephora.com/studded-kiss-lipstick-P387435?skuId=1621762').tags.create(name: "Lipstick")
Item.create(name:'Christian Louboutin Velvet Matte Lip Colour', description:'This Intensely rich color goes on with full coverage and sets with a soft touch matte finish. Formulated with a complex of natural oils and seed butters to enhance moisturize for up to four hours, it provides a protective layer against dryness. These lip colors are available in a universal shade palette, ranging from light to deep tones, across mid-tonal and bright hues of pinks to berries, reds and corals, and nudes and browns. ', image_url:'https://res.cloudinary.com/keep/image/fetch/t_post_large,f_auto/https://s3.amazonaws.com/production-ol-images/887940488d897592b9b964f4f68f6b5e.jpg', buy_url:'http://www.sephora.com/velvet-matte-lip-colour-P400560?skuId=1750165').tags.create(name: "Lipstick")
Item.create(name:'Guerlain KissKiss Creamy Satin Finish Lipstick', description:'This lipstick imparts covetable color and ultra-comfortable texture. Enriched with hydrating mango butter and hyaluronic acid spheres, it plumps lips, while its balanced hue and radiance offers a satiny, vibrant finish that’s budge-proof. '   ,  image_url:'http://beauty411.net/wp-content/uploads/2014/08/Guerlain-KissKiss-Lipstick-The-Pinks.png',     buy_url:'http://www.sephora.com/kisskiss-creamy-satin-finish-lipstick-P388222?skuId=1618131').tags.create(name: "Lipstick")
Item.create(name:'Bobbi Brown Shimmer Brick', description:'Achieve a glowing hint of shimmer with Bobbi Brown’s Shimmer Brick. This compact features five shades infused with superfine pigments that reflect radiance and light. Just dust all five shades lightly on the top of cheekbones where the light hits your face.',  image_url:'http://www.polyvore.com/cgi/img-set/BQcDAAAAAwoDanBnAAAABC5vdXQKFklHOGsyVkliNEJHUm5vVmExa1N3cWcAAAACaWQKAWUAAAAEc2l6ZQ.jpg', buy_url:'http://www.sephora.com/shimmer-brick-bronze-P270545?skuId=1780675').tags.create(name: "Blush")
Item.create(name:'Dior Blush Vibrant Colour Powder Blush',description:'This beautiful powder blush blends smoothly onto skin for a natural finish or it can be layered for a bold, dramatic statement.', image_url:'http://hudabeauty.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/DSC_4098.jpg',     buy_url:'http://www.sephora.com/diorblush-vibrant-colour-powder-blush-P382451?skuId=1558907').tags.create(name: "Blush")
Item.create(name:'Yves Saint Laurent BLUSH VOLUPTÈ - Heart Of Light Powder Blush', description:'Yves Saint Blush Volupté is a blush and highlighter that provides contouring and achieves a vibrant glow. Featuring “color light prism" technology, this makeup offers balanced consistency between how the blush looks and the application result. The higher saturation of color pigments offers intense color payoff, and the extra thin particles give a natural and buildable look. The Mother of Pearl color offers intense, "light" radiance, while the emollients leave a perfect, silky finish.',  image_url:'http://scontent-a.cdninstagram.com/hphotos-xaf1/t51.2885-15/10691890_813004992083966_131220964_a.jpg', buy_url:'http://www.sephora.com/blush-volupte-heart-of-light-powder-blush-P388641?skuId=1625508').tags.create(name: "Blush")
Item.create(name:'Miu Miu', description:'Miu Miu starts with an elegant, sensual floral—lily of the valley—composed of real jasmine, real rose absolute, and synthetic green notes. The soft, fresh, ingénue scent is set against a deep earth-toned background: the wood and pepper of akigalawood, an extract of patchouli. The akigalawood adds a rich, brooding mystery to the subtle sparkle of the floral. The surprising combination feels natural and timeless—flower and earth—but the effect created by the multi-faceted process is utterly contemporary.',image_url:'http://www.wonderlandmagazine.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/MiuMiu-The-First-Fragrance.jpg',buy_url:'http://www.sephora.com/miu-miu-P404286?skuId=1785682').tags.create(name: "Perfume")
Item.create(name:'Marc Jacobs Fragrances Decadence', description:'A sensual, luxurious, and woody fragrance, Decadence embodies the spirit of irreverent glamour. The fragrance opens with sultry top notes of Italian plum, iris flower, and saffron. The heart combines luxurious notes of Bulgarian rose, jasmine sambac, and orris. The indulgent dry down reveals the base notes of vetiver, papyrus woods, and liquid amber.',  image_url:'http://beautydesk.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/Marc-Jacobs_Decadence_Image-e1444249872266-400x337.jpg',buy_url:'http://www.sephora.com/decadence-P400783?skuId=1739762').tags.create(name: "Perfume")
Item.create(name:'Thierry Mugler Alien', description:'Discover Alien, radiant and mysterious, the elixir of absolute femininity. Be seduced by the soothing solar energy of this extraordinary fragrance from elsewhere. Luminous like a brilliant solar flower, the fragrance exudes a positive energy, charged with mystery. Evoking the scent of wood warmed by intense sunlight, Alien is sensual and intriguing, yet as soft and rich as the caress of cashmere', image_url:'https://alostouramagazine.files.wordpress.com/2014/05/thierry-mugler_alien-prestigious-giant-bottle-custom.jpg?w=1112'  ,buy_url:'http://www.sephora.com/alien-P196516?skuId=1040815').tags.create(name: "Perfume")
